data.description: This 1731 square foot single family home has 3 bedrooms and 2.0 bathrooms. This home is located at 1410 SW 12th Ct, Fort Lauderdale, FL 33312.
data.whatILove: Completely updated turn key home in highly desirable Shady Banks! Brand new METAL ROOF and silicone flat roof 2023 with straps and adhesive! New kitchen with waterfall upgraded QUARTZ slab and extra storage under the large quartz peninsula. Updated saltwater pool and hot tub with new Diamondbrite, LED lighting tile, pump, new salt system and has a gas heater. Gas Tankless Water Heater with never ending supply. New modern bathroom with large shower, new AC unit 2023 and duct work. New Lighting fixtures, newer appliances, pantry fridge and cabinets in combined laundry space Full hurricane impact rated windows, sliders and French doors. Fully fenced pet friendly yard. Tropical oasis backyard, Tiki hut with outdoor storage, wet bar, and travertine deck.  New mini split in master bedroom for extra cold nights.  Vivint alarm system and smart home features.  Top of the line New Age garage system in spacious garage. Large backyard with freshly cleaned palms, haas avocado, banana trees and a mature mango tree.  Bahama Shutters outside and new plantation shutters inside. Private storage space by pool with connections for cabana 1/2 bath. Steps from the Nee River with a park, preserve, basketball court, Tennis Court and baseball field in the neighborhood within just a few miles from the beach. No HOA. MUST SEE!
